{"tid":2336318,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"家庭入息中位數10年來首跌 工聯會：貧窮問題已響警號","createTime":"2020-12-22T13:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T15:13:59.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"685d25f328ef8bbb8c6d3346bc212c55b053ebeb","tid":2336318,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2830000/2834860/incomet72020_103_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2830000%2F2834860%2Fincomet72020_103_1024.jpg&h=4bbb7957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府扶貧委員會將於明日公布最新2019年貧窮報告。但工聯會九龍東總幹事鄧家彪指，該報告反映2019年數字，恐數據滯後，未能反映疫情下逼切的貧窮問題。<br />\n<br />\n鄧家彪表示，今年第3季家庭入息中位數，錄得10年來首次跌幅，由去年的$35,800，跌至今年的$33,700，即減$2,100收入，<span class=\"red\">跌約5.9%</span>，形容貧窮問題惡化已響起警號。<br />\n<br />\n鄧續說，家庭入息中位數收入減少，物價卻不跌反升。他指，統計處近日公布本年11月甲類消費物價指數，該指數持續高於反映中產消費的乙或丙類的消費物價指數，其中甲類食品指數（非外出用膳）更達131.2，遠高綜合物價指數的110.9，反映基層必要開支增，負擔日益沉重。<br />\n<br />\n基層消費物價指數<br />\n<br />\n年份 綜合消費物價指數 甲類 乙類 丙類<br />\n2011年 86.1 84.2 86.5 88<br />\n2015年 100.6 100.6 100.5 100.5<br />\n2019年 110.1 111.5 109.6 109.3<br />\n2020年11月 110.9 112.7 110.2 109.9<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n現年35歲的梁先生曾任設計師，疫情前月入有2萬元至2.5萬元，惟其公司2月倒閉，他失業半年搵工無回音，靠積蓄及送外賣勉強支撐一家四口。他冀政府除推失業援助金外，<span class=\"red\">可設無息貸款</span>，助失業人士度過難關。住劏房的單親母親王小姐指，疫情下收入減少，<span class=\"red\">業主卻加租800元</span>。<br />\n<br />\n鄧家彪促政府創造臨時抗疫所需職位，如喉管檢測等，助短期紓困；長遠則加徵物業空置稅及物業增值稅等，以抑止樓價。"},{"pid":"1f80f382c369a19890e6f5925a5660c911100ec8","tid":2336318,"uid":184787,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:31:14.000Z","msg":"班友訓撚左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2c4ff6082e280cc8f718900312363967d4a7c6","tid":2336318,"uid":128991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:33:56.000Z","msg":"原來立法會趕走咗泛民會令我變窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b144933f75c4c01cabd209deee0e2b4bd334cb1a","tid":2336318,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f80f382c369a19890e6f5925a5660c911100ec8","tid":2336318,"uid":184787,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:31:14.000Z","msg":"班友訓撚左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"人地工聯會啊"},{"pid":"bc0025a01364cddd0baea791b8888f9b2b4cdb55","tid":2336318,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:36:58.000Z","msg":"入咁撚多支那狗黎緊係跌啦"},{"pid":"508b054038dfe438873b8825e54899e28b1085db","tid":2336318,"uid":385411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:39:40.000Z","msg":"十幾年前已經響傻咗？"},{"pid":"cf676b7992eafe1985b293fa79d5ab3171e54357","tid":2336318,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"連續三個晴報post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8582de794d266e407c5546e95c5710698ae24356","tid":2336318,"uid":293937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"有邊一年冇響過?<br />\n響完啦,之後呢?"},{"pid":"415e8bc044c0040796321a0fc31f31b338b63939","tid":2336318,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:13:59.000Z","msg":"立法會點做野<br />\n建制派點做野"}]}